Requirements (versions are tested ones):

python      2.6.4, 2.6.2

pygobject   2.18.0, 2.16.1
pygtk       2.14.1
libglade    2.6.4

dnet        1.11
pylibpcap   0.5.1
ipy         0.70, 0.64


=== Linux ===

- for firewalling 'iptables' is need in the path.
- rfc2385 support in bgp needs following kernel options

CONFIG_TCP_MD5SIG=y



=== FreeBSD ===

- rfc2385 support in bgp needs following kernel options

options     IPSEC
device      crypto
options     TCP_SIGNATURE
